net.metro.analyze

Class RouteImport.WayPointSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.metro.analyze.RouteImport.WayPointSet
  • Enclosing class:
    RouteImport

    private class RouteImport.WayPointSet
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper class for individual waypoints that contain an ArrayList of WayPoints and their corresponding route id, route name, route path id, and route path name. These are later added to the SystemObjects database via the processDataSets() method.
    Author:
    Sean
